ving slept so comfortably while being in a winter bivouac … stay tuned … more informations the next weeks!\n\nI think the tents are already quite photogenic subjects for the foreground , aren´t they ???  INSERT INTO `dzmvb_options` (`option_id`, `option_name`, `option_value`, `autoload`) VALUES
